EXAMPLES:
```python
# Turn consumption example
player.turns = 1000  # Daily allocation
player.move_to_sector(sector_id=42)  # Costs 1 turn (modified by ship speed)
player.dock()  # Costs 1 turn
player.buy_commodity("ORE", 100)  # 0 turns while docked
player.sell_commodity("FUEL", 50)  # 0 turns while docked
player.undock()  # Costs 1 turn
# Remaining turns: ~997

# Combat resolution (defender pays no turns)
attacker.initiate_combat(defender)  # Attacker pays turns
# Combat resolved based on:
# - attacker.drones vs defender.drones
# - attacker.ship.firepower vs defender.ship.shields
# - Random tactical elements
# Defender turn count unchanged

# Colonization requirements
if player.credits >= 10000 and player.cargo.population >= 10000:
    player.colonize_planet(planet_id)
    player.credits -= 10000
    player.cargo.population -= 10000
    # Planet now owned, generates passive income
```
